Module com.game
Package com.game.models

Class SnakeModel

java.lang.Object
com.game.models.SnakeModel
public class SnakeModel extends Object
Snake Model is an all-in-one MVC model of the Snake's movement that handles The positions of its body and head, direction, and velocity.
Author:
Alfie Rushby-modified
